Of course, I'd say no.

00:09:17.730 --> 00:09:18.480
Maybe you did.

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:20.620
Maybe I've caught them.

00:09:20.620 --> 00:09:21.180
So you see.

00:09:21.180 --> 00:09:22.120
And now they're mad.

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:25.074
You have stolen
all of this stuff,

00:09:25.074 --> 00:09:26.740
and you are giving
it away to everybody.

00:09:26.740 --> 00:09:28.323
And we cannot make
any money for that.

00:09:28.323 --> 00:09:30.190
Well, see, this is
what I get to do.

00:09:30.190 --> 00:09:31.860
I said, no, that's
not how it works.

00:09:31.860 --> 00:09:37.240
Let me tell you how you
can write very good stuff,

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:41.220
