will make money at that.

00:09:48.926 --> 00:09:50.430
Well, isn't that interesting?

00:09:50.430 --> 00:09:54.120
So and the process of
doing all of these things,

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:58.130
I have learned a
simple step-by-step,

00:09:58.130 --> 00:10:07.920
that if I do these five things,
I can beat anybody at anything.

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:12.090
I can beat anybody at anything.

00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:13.450
So how do you do that?

00:10:13.450 --> 00:10:16.440
And I thank you for the lessons,
because you taught me this.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:18.710
It starts with telling stories.

00:10:18.710 --> 00:10:20.210
I tell stories.

