And I fix the problem for you.

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:30.750
And the more I tell
the story about how

00:10:30.750 --> 00:10:33.750
I can fix your problem,
the bigger, the better,

00:10:33.750 --> 00:10:35.520
the stronger the hero I am.

00:10:35.520 --> 00:10:36.630
What's your problem?

00:10:36.630 --> 00:10:37.830
Let me solve that problem.

00:10:37.830 --> 00:10:39.390
Let me fix that problem for you.

00:10:39.390 --> 00:10:42.390
And when I fix it, I
will be your champion.

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:43.370
I will be your hero.

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:44.790
Well, that's the basics.

00:10:44.790 --> 00:10:45.960
I tell stories.

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:48.890
And if I tell that
story more than anybody

00:10:48.890 --> 00:10:54.020
else who tells the same kind
of story, I can beat them.

00:10:54.020 --> 00:10:56.120
So if I tell a story,
and I tell it more,

00:10:56.120 --> 00:10:58.060
and then I have
to tell it better.

