find something good.

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:12.890
So I have to tell it better.

00:11:12.890 --> 00:11:13.610
I tell stories.

00:11:13.610 --> 00:11:14.230
I tell more.

00:11:14.230 --> 00:11:15.290
I tell it better.

