00:14:04.028 --> 00:14:05.210
I visited China for a while.

00:14:05.210 --> 00:14:06.455
I visited Korea for a while.

00:14:06.455 --> 00:14:08.120
I visited several
different countries

00:14:08.120 --> 00:14:10.310
as a visiting teacher, OK?

00:14:10.310 --> 00:14:11.350
Come teach us.

00:14:11.350 --> 00:14:12.980
And so I'm in Japan.

00:14:12.980 --> 00:14:16.120
And my boys, both of my
boys, are made in Japan.

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:18.210
It says, made in Japan here.

00:14:18.210 --> 00:14:19.840
We just don't show
that to people.

00:14:19.840 --> 00:14:22.540
My daughter was made in China
