00:14:22.540 --> 00:14:24.110
What can I say?

00:14:24.110 --> 00:14:27.980
And so my boys were nine
years old and six years old,

00:14:27.980 --> 00:14:31.070
and they were going
to a Japanese school.

00:14:31.070 --> 00:14:38.200
One day, they came home
from school with tears.

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:38.900
What's wrong?

00:14:38.900 --> 00:14:40.110
What's wrong?

00:14:40.110 --> 00:14:44.180
Well, Poppa, when we
are at school today,

00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:48.530
