Well, what could that be?

00:18:49.690 --> 00:18:52.460
I was in Russia.

00:18:52.460 --> 00:18:53.770
I was in Russia.

00:18:53.770 --> 00:18:56.100
I was teaching a class.

00:18:56.100 --> 00:18:59.490
This was during the Cold War.

00:18:59.490 --> 00:19:02.420
It was still 1989.

00:19:02.420 --> 00:19:04.100
And I'm teaching a class.

00:19:04.100 --> 00:19:07.390
There are probably this many
people in the classroom.

00:19:07.390 --> 00:19:10.400
They asked me to come teach
them how to teach English.

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:11.440
They were Russians.

00:19:11.440 --> 00:19:12.560
They were very, very good.

00:19:12.560 --> 00:19:15.620
Some of them spoke
English better than I did.

00:19:15.620 --> 00:19:19.020
Well, and here I am
teaching this class.

00:19:19.020 --> 00:19:23.590
And a man in a black suit
comes in with a little girl

00:19:23.590 --> 00:19:25.700
and yellow hair.

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:29.550
It looked like
Boris and Natasha.

00:19:29.550 --> 00:19:33.580
I don't know if you knew it
from Maxwell Smart, right?

00:19:33.580 --> 00:19:36.370
He was a KGB agent.

00:19:36.370 --> 00:19:38.750
He was a secret policeman.

00:19:38.750 --> 00:19:42.200
And I know that, because
everybody in the room

00:19:42.200 --> 00:19:46.050
