[WHISPERING] KGB, KGB.

00:19:46.050 --> 00:19:50.770
And when everybody in the room
whispers [WHISPERING] KGB, KGB,

00:19:50.770 --> 00:19:52.610
I can hear them, right?

00:19:52.610 --> 00:19:53.110
Try that.

00:19:53.110 --> 00:19:55.558
Everybody, try it.
[WHISPERING] KGB.

00:19:55.558 --> 00:19:57.010
Yeah, you see, we can hear that.

00:19:57.010 --> 00:19:59.180
And so after I
taught to that class,

00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:02.080
the KGB man came up to
me with his little girl.

00:20:02.080 --> 00:20:10.988
He said, Bill, Bill, I want to
take you out to meet a witch.

00:20:10.988 --> 00:20:14.240
Well, I've never
met a KGB agent.

00:20:14.240 --> 00:20:18.760
And now I get to
meet a witch, also.

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:21.270
And they put me in a car.

00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:24.120
And they drove me out
into the darkness.

00:20:24.120 --> 00:20:27.790
Have you ever seen the movie
"White Nights," "White Nights?"

00:20:27.790 --> 00:20:29.230
Now, I see a head.

00:20:29.230 --> 00:20:31.190
If you have not seen
the movie, go home,

00:20:31.190 --> 00:20:32.645
watch the movie, "White Nights."

00:20:32.645 --> 00:20:34.680
Baryshnikov, the
ballet dancer, right?

00:20:34.680 --> 00:20:36.927
He escapes from Russia.

00:20:36.927 --> 00:20:38.760
He runs away from
Russia-- the word defect--

00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:40.170
he runs away from Russia.

