And Gregory Hines goes
the other way, to Russia.

00:20:43.780 --> 00:20:46.410
Well, at the end of the
movie, Gregory Hines-- he's

00:20:46.410 --> 00:20:49.235
a tap dancer-- he's
in a black sedan.

00:20:49.235 --> 00:20:52.890
He's In a black car, and
they're driving him out.

00:20:52.890 --> 00:20:56.906
And you think, he is dead.

00:20:56.906 --> 00:20:59.140
They are going to kill him.

00:20:59.140 --> 00:21:02.860
That's what happened to me.

00:21:02.860 --> 00:21:05.870
I'm in a black car,
it's very, very dark,

00:21:05.870 --> 00:21:08.750
and they're taking me out
and into the darkness.

00:21:08.750 --> 00:21:10.580
Oh, I'm going to die.

00:21:10.580 --> 00:21:12.910
I was sure I was going to die.

00:21:12.910 --> 00:21:14.420
And the only thing
I could think of,

00:21:14.420 --> 00:21:17.725
I hope I meet the
witch before I die.

00:21:17.725 --> 00:21:18.225
[LAUGHTER]

00:21:18.225 --> 00:21:21.760
BILL BELEW: Otherwise,
why am I doing this?

00:21:21.760 --> 00:21:23.960
Well, when I met
the witch, we had

00:21:23.960 --> 00:21:29.600
this talk going back and forth.

00:21:29.600 --> 00:21:34.120
And the questions she asked
me were the same questions

00:21:34.120 --> 00:21:37.790
I was asked just
two weeks before.

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:40.190
I was in Moscow.

00:21:40.190 --> 00:21:42.072
Moscow was the only
Russian word I know.

00:21:42.072 --> 00:21:43.405
And that's not even said Moscow.

00:21:43.405 --> 00:21:45.080
It's Moskova, right?

00:21:45.080 --> 00:21:47.440
So I'm in Russia.

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:50.450
I'm in Red Square,
right in the very heart.

00:21:50.450 --> 00:21:52.550
There's a big red wall
and a big yellow building

00:21:52.550 --> 00:21:53.299
on the other side.

00:21:53.299 --> 00:21:55.080
There's dead Lenin, [MOANING].

00:21:55.080 --> 00:21:56.170
He's dead right there.

00:21:56.170 --> 00:21:57.600
And on the other
side of the wall,

00:21:57.600 --> 00:22:01.900
there is a school called
the Moscow Higher Party

00:22:01.900 --> 00:22:06.530
School of Communism,
the Moscow Higher Party

00:22:06.530 --> 00:22:08.090
School of Communism.

00:22:08.090 --> 00:22:16.200
And never, never had an American
been inside that school before.

00:22:16.200 --> 00:22:18.130
They invited me.

00:22:18.130 --> 00:22:19.330
Well, that's cool.

00:22:19.330 --> 00:22:23.400
I get to go inside the Moscow
High Party School of Communism.

00:22:23.400 --> 00:22:25.490
Well, they couldn't
just let me go.

00:22:25.490 --> 00:22:29.790
So they had to change my name
from William to Uil'yam, from

00:22:29.790 --> 00:22:31.075
Belew to Beloff.

00:22:31.075 --> 00:22:32.700
And then the middle
name was Ivanovich.

00:22:32.700 --> 00:22:34.074
It should have
been Leonardovich.

00:22:34.074 --> 00:22:36.360
So I'm Uil'yam Ivanovich Beloff.

00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:38.800
And they took me in there
and said, [RUSSIAN],

00:22:38.800 --> 00:22:40.240
and I just go on in.

00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:45.430
And they took me to a room where
I met a professor whose job it

00:22:45.430 --> 00:22:54.850
was to tell the world
what is communism.

00:22:54.850 --> 00:23:00.710
He had his fingers in the
entire world of communism,

00:23:00.710 --> 00:23:03.690
and I was invited
to talk to him.

00:23:03.690 --> 00:23:06.330
Well, the first day, we
were talking and talking.

00:23:06.330 --> 00:23:09.650
And he just comes after me.

00:23:09.650 --> 00:23:10.850
I'm just an English teacher.

00:23:10.850 --> 00:23:12.130
Help, help!

00:23:12.130 --> 00:23:13.720
And he wants to
know, what's better?

00:23:13.720 --> 00:23:16.830
Is it feudalism, where
people rule people?

00:23:16.830 --> 00:23:19.500
Is it imperialism, where
countries rule others?

00:23:19.500 --> 00:23:21.950
Is it nationalism, where
countries rule countries?

00:23:21.950 --> 00:23:24.530
Is it capitalism, where
money controls everything?

00:23:24.530 --> 00:23:28.172
Or is it Marxism,
this big idea where

